# ✨ About MindCraft

**MindCraft** is an **AI-powered study assistance application** built for engineering students who want smarter, faster, and more personalized learning experiences.

From generating study notes to answering academic queries in real time — MindCraft acts as your **personal AI tutor**, available 24/7 right from your phone.

> _"Don't just study harder — study smarter with MindCraft."_

This repository contains **all official Megaproject documentation** including research papers, reports, presentations, weekly diaries, and manuscripts submitted as part of the **2024–25 academic Megaproject.**

---

# 🔥 Key Highlights

- 🤖 **AI Study Assistant** – Get instant answers to academic questions powered by AI.
- 📚 **Smart Notes Generator** – Auto-generate structured notes from topics.
- 🎯 **Personalized Learning** – Adapts to the student's pace and syllabus.
- 📱 **Mobile App** – Fully functional cross-platform application.
- 🔒 **Secure & Private** – Student data handled responsibly.

